The number here is obviously 0.  Innocents wouldn't know anything worth torturing them over
<br />

<br />
<span style="font-style: italic">Do you just pick up people at random because of the religion they follow or the color of thier skin?</span>
<br />
I don't think I advocated picking people up for any reason.  Assuming the question is about who gets tortured, I'd say that the decision would need to be made by anyone with the full knowledge that what they were doing would likely result in them losing their jobs and serving jail time.
<br />

